commitResults.messageTitle: Modified README - Updated README and other files
Completed Level-1 Increment - Created a while loop to scan user input - Exit condition of "bye" - Echos the user input
Completed Level-2 Increment - Created a fixed size array to store input - Added an else-if condition to return the stored inputs
Completed Level-3 Increment - Created new classes Task and TaskList - Moved some logic in the main loop to TaskList - Added else-if statements to check for mark and unmark

Completed Level-4 Increment - Added Todo, Deadline and Event classes that inherit Task - Used the .substring() method to access the information in user input - Used the .split() method to access the information if user creates   deadline or event

Completed A-TextUiTesting - Added a few sample lines into input.txt - Created a EXPECTED.TXT file to match the input - Ran the runtest.sh file and kept failing despite same actual and   expected - Passed the test after installing dos2unix
Completed Level-5 Increment - Created BeeException class which extends exception - Generates a bee ascii art text along with the error message in the   case of incorrect outputs
Completed Level-6 Increment - Added delete functionality in TaskList - Refactored the TaskList code to use ArrayList<Task> - Minor bug fixes for the error handling in Bee
Completed A-Enums Increment - Added TaskClass and TaskAction enums to represent the elifs - Refactored the code to createTask and updateTask methods

Implemented Level-7 Increment - Changed if-else main block to switch statements for readability - Added loadTasksFromFile(), saveTasksToFile() and parseTask() - Program can now save the output to a file and read from there - Added new constructors in the task classes to help parseTask()
Completed Level-8 Increment - Changed Deadline class to store LocalDateTime for the deadline - Updated the createTask and parseTask logic to read the new format
Completed A-MoreOOP Increment - Created Parser, Storage and Ui classes - Extracted large chunk of code to those classes,  making code look   neater
Completed A-Packages Increment - Created a bee package and moved all the class files into the package
